-12|language=ja}}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:90%;\"| [[Billboard Japan#Billboard Japan charts|JPN Hot]]<br><ref>Billboard Japan Hot Albums:\n*{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard-japan.com/charts/detail?a=hot_albums&year=2019&month=06&day=17|title=Red Planet (Japan Edition)|publisher=Billboard Japan|date=2019-06-17|language=ja}}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:90%;\"| [[Billboard charts#Albums|US<br>World]]<br><ref>Billboard World Albums:\n*{{cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/charts/world-albums/2017-10-21|title=Red Diary Page.1|publisher=Billboard|date=2017-10-21}}</ref>\n|-\n! colspan=\"8\" | Korean\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''Red Ickle''\n|\n*Released: April 22, 2016\n*Label: Shofar Music\n*Formats: CD, digital download, streaming\n{{hidden|Track listing|\n#Chocolate {{small|({{lang|ko|\ucd08\ucf5c\ub9bf}})}}\n#'''Fight Day''' {{small|({{lang|ko|\uc2f8\uc6b4\ub0a0}})}}\n#'''Ring''' {{small|({{lang|ko|\ubc18\uc9c0}})}}\n#'''Grumpy''' {{small|({{lang|ko|\uc2ec\uc220}})}}\n#Occasionally {{small|({{lang|ko|\uac00\ub054\uc529}})}}\n}}\n| 30 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014\n|\n*KOR: 659<ref>{{cite web|url=http://gaonchart.co.kr/main/section/chart/album.gaon?nationGbn=T&serviceGbn=&targetTime=10&hitYear=2016&termGbn=month|title=2016\ub144 10\uc6d4 Album Chart}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''Red Diary Page.1''\n|\n*Released: September 28, 2017\n*Label: Shofar Music\n*Formats: CD, digital download, streaming\n{{hidden|Track listing|\n#'''Some''' {{small|({{lang|ko|\uc378\ud0c8\uaebc\uc57c}})}}\n#Blue\n#Fix Me {{small|({{lang|ko|\uace0\uccd0\uc8fc\uc138\uc694}})}}\n#Imagine {{small|({{lang|ko|\uc0c1\uc0c1}})}}\n#'''To My Youth''' {{small|({{lang|ko|\ub098\uc758 \uc0ac\ucd98\uae30\uc5d0\uac8c}})}}\n}}\n| 7 || \u2014 || \u2014 || 9\n|\n*KOR: 13,277<!--12,098 + 1,179--><ref>Cumulative sales of ''Red Diary Page.1'':\n*{{cite web|url=http://gaonchart.co.kr/main/section/chart/album.gaon?nationGbn=T&serviceGbn=&targetTime=12&hitYear=2017